on"><s>Cells are straight rods.</s><s>Gram-negative.</s><s>Spores are not formed.</s><s>Grow aerobically and anaerobically only with nitrate.</s><s>Moderately thermophilic member of the domain <em>Bacteria</em>, class <em>β</em>-<em>Proteobacteria</em>.</s><s>Organic acids serve as main substrates.</s></p><p class="description"><s>The type species is <em>Petrobacter succinatimandens</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>